    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff</strong> <strong>pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> and cut into 1 rectangle per person</p><p>Add the<strong> pastry rectangle[s] </strong>to the tray[s] and score a 1cm border around the edge of the pastry with a knife</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until puffed up, golden and cooked through – these are your <strong>pie lids</strong></p>",
